l] which they smelt in the fire in order to make ornaments or utensils, [there rises] scum. In this way does God set forth the parable of truth and falsehood: for, as far as the scum is concerned, it passes away as [does all] dross; but that which is of benefit to man abides on earth. In this way does God set forth the parables","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1724.mp3","surahId":13,"words":[{"id":19899,"position":1,"arabic":"أَنزَلَ","translation":"তিনি বর্ষণ করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19900,"position":2,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19901,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱلسَّمَآءِ","translation":"আকাশ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19902,"position":4,"arabic":"مَآءًۭ","translation":"পানি","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19903,"position":5,"arabic":"فَسَالَتْ","translation":"ফলে প্লাবিত হয়","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19904,"position":6,"arabic":"أَوْدِيَةٌۢ","translation":"উপত্যকাসমূহ","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19905,"position":7,"arabic":"بِقَدَرِهَا","translation":"তার পরিমাণ অনুসারে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19906,"position":8,"arabic":"فَٱحْتَمَلَ","translation":"অতঃপর বহন করে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19907,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلسَّيْلُ","translation":"প্লাবন","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19908,"position":10,"arabic":"زَبَدًۭا","translation":"ফেনা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19909,"position":11,"arabic":"رَّابِيًۭا ۚ","translation":"উপরিভাগে","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19911,"position":12,"arabic":"وَمِمَّا","translation":"এবং তা থেকেও যা","audioUrl":"wbw/013_017_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":19912,"position":13,